data.description:
Introducing a blank canvas for your dream home! This 2 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath, 2427 square foot property offers a world of possibilities for those with a creative vision and entrepreneurial aspirations.  Located in the Urban Arts Loft community of Lake Worth Beach, this property features a freshly painted interior and new LVP flooring. The building is certified energy efficient and features impact glass, a tankless water heater, gas range and dryer.  HOA includes exterior maintenance, exterior insurance, roof maintenance, landscaping, irrigation, parking lots & lights, fire sprinkler system & monitoring. Downtown Lake Worth Beach is a short stroll away and offers a vibrant downtown with restaurants, eclectic stores, and access to local activities. **Income restrictions do apply for all buyers. 

Seize the opportunity to own a property that aligns with your professional ambitions & offers a lifestyle of comfort and recreation. Welcome to your next home where work and play coexist harmoniously.
